---
source: crates/runtime/tests/models/search.rs
description: "SELECT subject FROM vector_search(qs, 'second', answer) order by score desc LIMIT 4"
---
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                               |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).subject                                                      |
|               |   Sort: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).score DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=4                                  |
|               |     Projection: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).subject, vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).score |
|               |       TableScan: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer) projection=[score, subject]                             |
| physical_plan | ProjectionExec: expr=[subject@0 as subject]                                                                        |
|               |   SortPreservingMergeExec: [score@1 DESC], fetch=4                                                                 |
|               |     SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[score@1 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                     |
|               |       ProjectionExec: expr=[subject@0 as subject, 1 - distance@1 as score]                                         |
|               |         CooperativeExec                                                                                            |
|               |           RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                     |
|               |             BytesProcessedExec                                                                                     |
|               |               CooperativeExec                                                                                      |
|               |                 S3VectorsQueryExec: limit=100                                                                      |
|               |                                                                                                                    |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
